{
  "texts": [
    "A dynamic threshold is designed through homeostasis.",
    "The adaptive threshold and lateral inhibition help a specific group of neurons to respond to a particular stimulus 42.",
    "The network is tested on the MNIST data-set.",
    "It achieves a maximum of 93.5% accuracy with 300 output neurons.",
    "A system-level simulation shows that the designed device can tolerate parameter variation up to 50% of the standard deviation of parameter values."
  ]
}